    <h1>Using the Command Line - Simple File Operations and Navigation</h1>
    <ul>
        <li><i>mkdir</i> - create directory</li>
        <code>mkdir python_examples</code>
        <li><i>cd</i> - change directory </li>
        <code>cd python_examples</code>
        <li><i>ls</i> - show contents of current directory</li>
        <li><i>python</i> - execute a Python file </li>
